// TESTY MANUALNE


//1
    Scenario: "Adding category properly"
    1.Click on add category button on side panel
    2.Complete data correctly
    3.New category should be visible on side panel


//2
    Scenario: "Adding category wrongly"
    1.Click on add category button on side panel
    2.Complete data wrongly
    3.Application should display information about not adding category
    4.New category should not be visible on side panel


//3
    Scenario: "Adding task properly"
    1.Click on add task button on side panel
    2.Complete data correctly
    3.New task should be visible on side panel


//4
    Scenario: "Adding task wrongly"
    1.Click on add task button on side panel
    2.Complete data wrongly
    3.Application should display information about not adding task
    4.New task should not be visible on side panel


//5
    Scenario: "Assign task to specific day properly"
    1.Click on specific day
    2.Complete data correctly
    3.New task should be visible in specific day


//6
    Scenario: "Assign task to specific day wrongly"
    1.Click on specific day
    2.Complete data wrongly
    3.Application should display information about not adding task
    4.New task should not be visible in specific day


//7
    Scenario: "Unassign task from specific day"
    1.Click on task in specific day
    2.Click on unassign button
    3.Task should not be visible in specific day


//8
    Scenario: "Move assigned task to other day"
    1.Drag task from one day to other
    2.Task should be in other day


//9
    Scenario: "Delete task"
    1.Click on task on side panel
    2.Click delete task
    3.Task should disappear from side panel
    4.Task should not disappear from days


//10
    Scenario: "Hide task"
    1.Click on task on side panel
    2.Click hide task
    3.Task should disappear from days in planner



}